Neith Hunter https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Neith_Hunter 0 Neith Andrina Hunter (born December 3, 1960) is an American model and actress. She began her modeling career in the 1980s in her home town of San Francisco, California, where she was discovered as a teen by John Casablancas, she was the first graduate of his exclusive model training center. French couturier Hubert de Givenchy offered her an exclusive contract to work for his House of Givenchy in Paris. She would later appear in several films, including Fright Night 2 (1988) and Silent Night, Deadly Night 4: Initiation (1990).
